{"tid":235010,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屌呀 鮑魚炒飯無鮑魚？","createTime":"2017-05-08T16:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T18:13:03.000Z","uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b1aa1cebf4f9ebb7f303252712e2067628f8aa","tid":235010,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"鮑魚炒飯無鮑魚葵涌酒樓違商品說明條例被罰5千元<br />\n<br />\n位於葵涌新葵興廣場的酒樓「茗苑宴會廳」，因售賣的一款炒飯，因註明附有「鮑魚」，但被證實飯內並無鮑魚，在西九龍裁判法院被裁定違反《商品說明條例》，被判罰款5千元。<br />\n<br />\n海關早前接獲舉報，於去年8月到這間酒樓進行試購行動，發現餐牌上一款註明附有鮑魚的炒飯。經政府化驗所檢測後，證實炒飯內並未附有鮑魚，與餐牌上顯示的商品說明不符。本台致電酒樓，查詢會否更改餐牌時，對方不作回應。<br />\n<br />\n海關提醒商戶遵守《條例》的規定，而消費者亦應光顧信譽良好的商戶，如果違法，一經定罪，最高可被判罰款50萬元及監禁5年。"},{"pid":"c38a84cca3aa4d37b8909495b16d94523c97c6c5","tid":235010,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"菠蘿包都無菠蘿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687fefb098203f8051af444cec9617ebe64f7708","tid":235010,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菠蘿包都無菠蘿啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1609642403b1c9c91c9264c7c59c3fbc79a66d0a","tid":235010,"uid":43979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"約人打交都無人啦=.="},{"pid":"769aa80b00f60bf40193703770e10d8a4b9c50c0","tid":235010,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約人打交都無人啦=.=</blockquote><br />\n9.9"},{"pid":"183bdc779f63b6e0690f1fdd36b2164d9a9c71e6","tid":235010,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>約人打交都無人啦=.=</blockquote><br />\nGap囝話佢吾系生番牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982927fb3f5d9950e352e3462035f9ac38abb559","tid":235010,"uid":225